
<div class="container">
  <div class="breed-description">
    <h5>Bernedoodles</h5>
    <div class="fb-like" data-href="http://localhost:3000" data-width="20px" data-layout="standard" data-action="like" data-show-faces="true" data-share="true"></div>
    <p>
      Looking for a family dog? Bernedoodles are a mix between a  Bernese Mountain Dog and a Poodle. They are fun, athletic, entertaining, loyal, friendly, and great with children. They range from 50 pounds to 110 pounds.
      In addition to being lovable they don't shed!
    </p>
  </div>
  <br>
  <div class="owl-carousel" id = "carousel-home">
    <% @pictures.each do |picture| %>
      <div class="item"><%= image_tag picture.name.url(:medium) %> </div>
    <% end %>
  </div>
</div>
